---
// Who Chooses What Section
---

<div id="who-chooses-what" class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
      Which One Fits Your Situation?
    </h2>

    <!-- Two Cards Side by Side -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
      
      <!-- Swica Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Swica — choose if you want:</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Strong wellness benefits (CHF 1,300/yr with Completa Forte)</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">BestMed / private worldwide options</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">More flexibility on pre-existing conditions</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">24/7 English support; excellent app</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Helsana Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-gray-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Helsana — choose if you want:</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Balanced premium vs coverage</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Good overall coverage + strong outpatient (Primeo)</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Very easy online applications</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Fast onboarding; broad networks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footnote -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
        <em>There's no universal winner — your <strong>age</strong>, <strong>canton</strong>, <strong>franchise</strong>, model and <strong>health</strong> decide the best fit.</em>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
